{"tid":437361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲領盟國阻中國滲透大學","createTime":"2017-10-16T02:51:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T14:09:06.000Z","uid":53379,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7d5dd5645e269f8d2b1679810aff87f70ef04a8e","tid":437361,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:51:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">澳洲領盟國阻中國滲透大學</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報導稱，澳洲正帶領西方盟國，防止中國官方影響力滲透西方國家的大學及專上學府。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲廣播公司報導稱，澳洲情報機構「觀察」到中國官方正在「攻擊」(Attack) 美國、英國、加拿大、澳洲和新西蘭的學術自由，已經循外交和情報途徑探討，包括由上述國家組成的「五眼聯盟」應否採取集體措施，回應「攻擊」。<br />\n<br />\n報導稱，澳洲在事件中，採取「領導的角色」。<br />\n<br />\n較早前，外交部秘書長阿當森 (Frances Adamson) 罕有地就中國官方在大學的活動表達關注，警告澳洲大學面對外國勢力干預，必須具備抵抗能力。<br />\n<br />\n阿當森的講話是在阿德雷德大學孔子學院發表。<br />\n<br />\n阿當森強調：「從學生、講師到政客，任何人的沉默，是對我們價值觀的冒犯。」<br />\n<br />\n報導稱，美國的中國學生組織經常企圖打壓不同於北京立場的異見聲音。8 月，英國劍橋大學出版社應中國政府要求，刪除「敏感」文章。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sbs.com.au/yourlanguage/cantonese/zh-hant/article/2017/10/16/bao-dao-ao-zhou-ling-meng-guo-zu-zhong-guo-shen-tou-da-xue?language=zh-hant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Fyourlanguage%2Fcantonese%2Fzh-hant%2Farticle%2F2017%2F10%2F16%2Fbao-dao-ao-zhou-ling-meng-guo-zu-zhong-guo-shen-tou-da-xue%3Flanguage%3Dzh-hant&d=oakFjxmgHF0hgzt0QCe%2FC7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=183c5389\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.sbs.com.au/yourlanguage/cantonese/zh-hant/article/2017/10/16/bao-dao-ao-zhou-ling-meng-guo-zu-zhong-guo-shen-tou-da-xue?language=zh-hant</a>"},{"pid":"342f8a97f5858fdcb8f594ea3e61fceaa41fa77f","tid":437361,"uid":54959,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:54:13.000Z","msg":"阿當森的講話是在阿德雷德大學孔子學院發表。<br />\n<br />\n係人哋個場當眾兜巴星，落撚晒人哋面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" cla